00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:12,045
So there's obviously a certain point where people get interested and they do care.

646
00:29:14,042 --> 00:29:16,584
But I think often that's not the problem for the game developers,

647
00:29:16,604 --> 00:29:18,625
because again, that's your experience,

648
00:29:18,665 --> 00:29:21,227
how you as a consumer usually interact with those things.

649
00:29:21,807 --> 00:29:24,128
Once you're interested, you know how to keep up to date,

650
00:29:24,269 --> 00:29:28,471
but the big majority of people just getting them on board is the challenge.

651
00:29:28,491 --> 00:29:39,895
Thank you.

